Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:38.67,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}呻きと声を挙げ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:45.88,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I'm gonna live out my life untamed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:17.53,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}たった―つのこの身焦がして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:22.73,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}血が枯れはてるまで進む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:32.13,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}遠い空から反る光もこの身に当たり消え
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:34.67,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}散ってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:42.35,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}荒ぶる波動を内に抱えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:56.25,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}握り締めた手の疼きは誰も知るはずなく！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:59.06,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}ぶち壊せ Break & Peace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:02.58,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}音も無く迫る闇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:07.98,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}光を灯す為 今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.30,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}ぶち壊すFate & Fear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:13.91,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生まれ持った衝動で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:20.30,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}全てを掴み獲れ今すぐ ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:24.04,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}真実を手に!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:32.30,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}扣下击断烦恼的扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:36.70,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毫无用处的自尊在垃圾回收日舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:41.70,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}猎取一切的武士疯狂起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:45.43,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}内燃机频频轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.79,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍将延续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:51.95,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使是糜烂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:56.65,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在叹息之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:03:00.53,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}跟随神风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:03.07,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}向着未知之处前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:08.07,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鼎沸的热情与
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:13.27,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}熏染的灵魂勒紧胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:17.73,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}如同燃烧的火焰般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:20.25,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能在此找到自己的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.64,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}雷达之下寻找自己的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:30.10,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起钢刃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:38.67,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}纵情呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:45.88,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}继续这不羁的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:17.53,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃焦这唯一的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:22.73,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}前进直到血干枯之时
